<p class="ql-align-justify">健身房的勐男，再搭一条金链子，稳稳的大哥风范：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200806/5bef5b73b41f4ac4800ecb9d2bb301f3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
