<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200806/5204f406679c4ebdb3cc696c1733957c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">勐男犯事进局子的身影，居然也有点莫名的可爱？</p>
