<p class="ql-align-justify">“这不就是金刚芭比吗？还扎了两个双马尾！”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200806/f386feb2af8c42a88f26013641af66c4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
